org.nerd4j.csv.writer.binding

Interface ModelToCSVBinderFactory<Model>

  • Type Parameters:
    Model - type of the model parsed by the binder.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractModelToCSVBinderFactory, ArrayToCSVBinderFactory, BeanToCSVBinderFactory, MapToCSVBinderFactory

    public interface ModelToCSVBinderFactory<Model>
    Represents a Factory able to build and configure ModelToCSVBinders which reads data models and provides CSV record fields in the right order.
    Author:
    Nerd4j Team

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      ModelToCSVBinder<Model> getModelToCSVBinder(CSVWriterMetadata<Model> configuration)
      Returns a new CSV model binder which parses the data model and returns the CSV fields in the required order.

      • getModelToCSVBinder

        ModelToCSVBinder<Model> getModelToCSVBinder(CSVWriterMetadata<Model> configuration)
                                            throws ModelToCSVBindingException
        Returns a new CSV model binder which parses the data model and returns the CSV fields in the required order.
        Parameters:
        configuration - used to configure the binding.
        Returns:
        a new CSV model binder.
        Throws:
        ModelToCSVBindingException - if binding configuration is inconsistent.
